** What success looks like in this role: **

  * Private Label Services Support 
  * Transformation Services calls, installing and servicing PCs, and PC peripherals and/or electronic equipment. 
  * Takes service calls and performs incident specific activities as directed by Help Desk, Service Desk or script 
  * May perform routine installs, moves, adds and changes as part of a directed team, including Complex desktop and laptop break fix work, Whole unit replacement, Simple desktop printer fixes, Load software with a script. 
  * Performs scripted image loading, unit diagnostics and replaceable unit swapping. 
  * Perform troubleshooting by running basic diagnostics and performs basic module replacement on PCs, servers and peripherals 
  * Performs preventative maintenance activities on certain products as directed 
  * Maintains a high degree of professionalism in actions, demeanor and dress. 
  * Ensures customer satisfaction throughout 
  * Ensures client specific Service Level Agreements are met and incident and request tickets are updated accordingly within the ticketing system 
  * May provide Smart hands support using augmented reality. 
  * May Maintaining stocks/ inventory at client’s site (if applicable) 

#LI-AS1

** You will be successful in this role if you have: **

  * • High school degree required 
  * Minimum 1-2 Years of hands-on experience with laptop and desktop break-fix 
  * Computer-building background experience preferred. 
  * A+ certification a plus 
  * Specific Manufacturer certification and/or training as required., i.e. EMC, Dell, Cisco, Microsoft, Unisys. COMPTIA, and NETWORKPLUS 
  * General knowledge of desktop hardware and software including basic knowledge of Microsoft applications 
  * Basic mechanical skills and understanding of electrostatic discharge (ESD) procedures 
  * Training and/or vendor certifications as required including completion of Core Training 
  * Ability to resolve basic / non-complex problems as directed 
  * Police or criminal background verification clearance may be required 

